data.description: This beautiful Sunnyslope home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a stunning in ground pool. The open floor plan includes a formal living/dining area and a kitchen, nook, and large family room with a cozy wood burning fireplace. Upgraded wood laminate throughout downstairs, with tile floors.  The original bedroom was expanded by 228 SqFt thus, including a large walk-in closet - 14 x7.5'! - two velux skylights, ceiling fans. Beautiful large front yard, located in a cul-de-sac corner for privacy. Close to schools, shopping and easy commute access.
